%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:47:04 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/infiniband-vs-rocev2-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/22/infiniband-vs-rocev2-차이점-정리.png" type="image/png" length="20442" /> </item> <item> <title>분산 학습 병렬화와 집합 통신 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>집합 통신 연산과 Data·Tensor·Pipeline·Expert 병렬화, ZeRO·FSDP 샤딩, 병렬화별 NVLink·InfiniBand 링크 매핑을 표로 비교</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B3%91%EB%A0%AC%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:47:04 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="true">https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/%EB%B6%84%EC%82%B0-%ED%95%99%EC%8A%B5-%EB%B3%91%EB%A0%AC%ED%99%94%EC%99%80-%EC%A7%91%ED%95%A9-%ED%86%B5%EC%8B%A0-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</guid> <enclosure url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/assets/images/social/blog/2026/07/22/분산-학습-병렬화와-집합-통신-정리.png" type="image/png" length="13420" /> </item> <item> <title>쿠버네티스 GPU 스케줄링 정리</title> <author>Jeongwon Lee</author> <category>AI</category> <description>기본 스케줄러가 GPU를 모르는 문제부터 device plugin 등록, GPU Operator 구성요소, time-slicing과 MIG, DRA 성숙도, gang scheduling과 DCGM 지표까지 정리</description> <link>https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/blog/2026/07/22/%EC%BF%A0%EB%B2%84%EB%84%A4%ED%8B%B0%EC%8A%A4-gpu-%EC%8A%A4%EC%BC%80%EC%A4%84%EB%A7%81-%EC%A0%95%EB%A6%AC/</link> <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 19:47:04 +0000</pubDate> <source url="https://dotoryeee.github.io/blog/feed_rss_created.xml">dotoryeee's blog</source><guid isPermaLink="t